text: "Act Naturally" is a 1963 song by country singer Buck Owens and went to number 1 on the Billboard Country singles chart. It has been covered by The Beatles, Loretta Lynn, Dwight Yoakam. The 1989 country duet version with Ringo Starr went to number 50 on the Canadian Country Tracks chart and was nominated for a Grammy Award in 1990.
